{"article_id":"ZCVblG7VfnNAZFt5","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Donald Trump offered his fellow Republicans a new slogan in their fight for border wall funding","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"that has shut down parts of the government for 33 days .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"\" BUILD A WALL","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"& CRIME WILL FALL ! \"","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"Trump said Wednesday on Twitter .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"\" This is the new theme , for two years","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"until the Wall is finished","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"( under construction now ) ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"of the Republican Party . \"","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"The new approach signals a return","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"to focus on Trump ' s claim","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"that the lack of a physical barrier along the southern border results in crime after a short period","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"where the White House sought to cast the situation as a humanitarian crisis","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"that a wall could help rectify .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"On Tuesday , people close to the president offered two different views of what he might concede in a possible negotiation .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"One said","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"Trump wouldn ' t accept any deal","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"that didn ' t deliver the full $ 5.7 billion in funding for a border wall","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"that he seeks .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"Another said","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"he ' d be willing to reduce that amount","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"if Democrats come up with concessions of their own .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"The diverging views echo complaints from Democrats ,","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"who have said","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"it ' s impossible to negotiate with Trump","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"because he and his representatives are at odds","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"and make shifting offers","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"that are subject to change at any time .","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"And they ' re not alone in that frustration .","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell stayed silent for the first weeks of the shutdown","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"after Trump suddenly reversed course in December","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"and rejected a spending bill","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"the Republican-led Senate had passed .","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"The first signs of movement from the Senate","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"to reopen the government","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"came Tuesday ,","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"when McConnell , a Kentucky Republican , and Minority Leader Chuck Schumer , a New York Democrat , agreed to vote on rival proposals","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"to end the standoff for the first time","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"since the funding lapse began last month .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"Lawmakers will hold the two separate votes on Thursday :","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"one on Trump ' s plan","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"that includes $ 5.7 billion for border wall funding ;","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"the other on a Democratic proposal","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"that would reopen shuttered agencies through Feb. 8","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"while both sides seek consensus on how to better secure the border .","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"Yet Trump has threatened to veto any measure","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"that doesn ' t fully fund his wall .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"Democrats likely have the votes","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"to block his bill ,","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"and the Democratic proposal would need to win support of 13 Republicans along with every Democrat","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"just to take up that measure .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"On Wednesday , Trump appeared to focus on the marketing of his wall for the GOP .","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"\" BUILD A WALL","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"& CRIME WILL FALL !","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"This is the new theme , for two years","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"until the Wall is finished","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"( under construction now ) ,","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"of the Republican Party .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"Use it","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"and pray ! \"","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"he wrote on Twitter .","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"Even as he digs in on his pro-wall rhetoric ,","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"Trump isn ' t ruling out concessions on significant issues .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"Those potentially include permanent status for young undocumented immigrants","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"who were brought to the U.S. as children ,","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"one of the people said ,","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"though that would likely carry a high price ,","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"according to a third person familiar with the president ' s thinking .","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"They requested anonymity","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"to discuss White House internal deliberations on the shutdown strategy .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"Trump has so far been unwavering in his demand for the $ 5.7 billion","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"and has given no public indication","depth":15},{"id":72,"text":"that he ' s willing to settle for a smaller amount .","depth":15},{"id":73,"text":"And he won ' t offer additional concessions","depth":15},{"id":74,"text":"until House Democrats put forward a proposal","depth":16},{"id":75,"text":"he considers a serious effort","depth":17},{"id":76,"text":"to break the impasse","depth":18},{"id":77,"text":"that has now stretched into a second month ,","depth":18},{"id":78,"text":"one of the people said .","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"Trump would only agree to lower his demand","depth":15},{"id":80,"text":"if Homeland Security officials","depth":17},{"id":81,"text":"who ' ve been advising him on border security","depth":17},{"id":82,"text":"signed off on it ,","depth":16},{"id":83,"text":"according to the person .","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"The president views the proposal","depth":17},{"id":85,"text":"he made over the weekend","depth":17},{"id":86,"text":"as an opening offer","depth":16},{"id":87,"text":"and is ready to work out a compromise","depth":16},{"id":88,"text":"if Democrats give ground ,","depth":16},{"id":89,"text":"aides say .","depth":14},{"id":90,"text":"Congressional Democrats rebuffed the plan ,","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"which would have provided three years of protections for the young immigrants ,","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"known as Dreamers .","depth":14},{"id":93,"text":"House Speaker Nancy Pelosi and Schumer have argued","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"the president ' s plan ,","depth":15},{"id":95,"text":"unveiled in a weekend address ,","depth":15},{"id":96,"text":"doesn ' t go far enough","depth":15},{"id":97,"text":"to justify what they argue","depth":16},{"id":98,"text":"is wasteful and immoral spending on a border wall .","depth":16},{"id":99,"text":"Trump doesn ' t feel the Democrats ' current proposal","depth":14},{"id":100,"text":"to provide additional funding for border security","depth":14},{"id":101,"text":"serious enough","depth":14},{"id":102,"text":"to counter ,","depth":14},{"id":103,"text":"one of the people said .","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"That ' s led to frustration within the West Wing ,","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"where aides believe","depth":14},{"id":106,"text":"that Pelosi and Schumer are instructing moderate members of their party not to negotiate with the White House on a possible compromise .","depth":14},{"id":107,"text":"White House senior adviser Jared Kushner and Vice President Mike Pence have sought to court Democrats in recent days in a series of phone calls and meetings ,","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"hoping to encourage them to break from their leadership .","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"Within the White House , aides understand","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"that the president ' s proposal will struggle to get to 60 votes .","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"But","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"even if his legislation fails ,","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"he may not necessarily move forward with an emergency declaration","depth":14},{"id":114,"text":"that would attempt to circumvent Congress","depth":15},{"id":115,"text":"by tapping unspent appropriations for border wall funding .","depth":15},{"id":116,"text":"That ' s partly because some in the administration believe","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"doing so would let Democrats off the hook in a fight over immigration","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"that some in the White House believe","depth":14},{"id":119,"text":"helps Trump politically .","depth":14},{"id":120,"text":"As Democratic leaders encourage their members not to engage with the administration ,","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"the president has warned","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"that the shutdown could continue to extend for a significant period of time","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"Schumer said","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"the Democratic plan","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"to fund agencies through Feb. 8","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"has the benefit","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"of ensuring federal workers get paid","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"and that agencies restore services ,","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"even if just a few weeks of operations would be guaranteed","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"as negotiations continue .","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"\" It will allow us to then debate","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"-- without hostage-taking ,","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"without temper tantrums ,","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"without anything --","depth":13},{"id":135,"text":"how we can best do border security ,","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"get that done hopefully by Feb. 8th ,","depth":13},{"id":137,"text":"and keep the government open , \"","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"Schumer said on the Senate floor .","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"McConnell called the White House plan a \" bold , comprehensive \" offer","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"and the only one","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"Trump is likely to sign .","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"Schumer ' s proposal passed the House this month , but with a veto threat from the White House .","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"There is some prospect of Senate Republican defections in favor of the Democratic plan","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"when the votes occur later this week .","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"Some Republicans in the chamber","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"-- including Cory Gardner of Colorado , Susan Collins of Maine and Lamar Alexander of Tennessee --","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"have been pressing for action","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"that would end the shutdown , now in its 33rd day , at least temporarily .","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"Yet","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"unless Trump changes his opposition","depth":13},{"id":151,"text":"it could be hard to get the votes to override his veto .","depth":13},{"id":152,"text":"It would take 20 Republicans in the Senate to vote with all 47 Democrats and Independents","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"to reach a two-thirds vote for an override .","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"In the House , 237 lawmakers voted in favor of the legislation , well short of the 290","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"needed","depth":11},{"id":156,"text":"to override a veto in that chamber .","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"Trump ' s proposal faces strong objections from Democrats","depth":9},{"id":158,"text":"who oppose the wall and some immigration law changes","depth":10},{"id":159,"text":"that include new asylum limits for Central American minors .","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"The Trump bill includes a provision","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"to ban nationals of El Salvador , Guatemala or Honduras","depth":13},{"id":162,"text":"who are under 18 years old","depth":13},{"id":163,"text":"from eligibility for asylum","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"unless they submit applications at a processing center in Central America .","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"That means they can not apply in the U.S.","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"if they flee their home countries","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"because of gang violence ,","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"as many have done .","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"As an olive branch to Democrats , the Trump proposal includes the provisional three-year work permits for Dreamers and those","depth":9},{"id":170,"text":"who have Temporary Protected Status .","depth":9},{"id":171,"text":"Trump has sought to end both programs .","depth":9},{"id":172,"text":"The new legislation , however , would only apply the DACA extension to those young immigrants","depth":13},{"id":173,"text":"currently receiving protections ,","depth":13},{"id":174,"text":"and not those","depth":13},{"id":175,"text":"who might be eligible","depth":14},{"id":176,"text":"to qualify ,","depth":14},{"id":177,"text":"as would be allowed under a previous bipartisan proposal","depth":12},{"id":178,"text":"called the Bridge Act .","depth":12},{"id":179,"text":"The new legislation would leave out hundreds of thousands of undocumented immigrants","depth":11},{"id":180,"text":"brought to the U.S. as children .","depth":11},{"id":181,"text":"Material from Bloomberg wire services was used in this story .","depth":1}],"relations":[{"parent":363,"left":362,"right":181,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":362,"left":195,"right":361,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":190,"right":194,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":190,"left":183,"right":189,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":183,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":189,"left":185,"right":188,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,